text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to get rid of a rash between your legs?
text.Response A: I would recommend seeing a doctor. This is something that you should not try to treat on your own. There are many different types of rashes, and some can be very serious. I would recommend seeing a doctor as soon as possible.
text.Response B: Yes, I can. The best way to get rid of a rash is to use an anti-fungal cream. You can find these at your local pharmacy.

meta.preamble_a: Respond in a cautious, defensive and uncertain way, as if you are unfamilar with the topic.
